tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_execution_progress (
    execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255),
    execution_status VARCHAR(50),
    execution_start TIMESTAMP,
    execution_end TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    execution_id INT,
    result_data JSONB,
    result_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (execution_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_execution_progress(execution_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Algorithms (
    Algorithm_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Algorithm_Name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    Execution_Time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    Result_BLOB BYTEA
);

CREATE TABLE Execution_Steps (
    Step_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Algorithm_ID INT NOT NULL,
    Step_Description TEXT,
    Step_Result BLOB,
    FOREIGN KEY (Algorithm_ID) REFERENCES Quantum_Algorithms(Algorithm_ID)
);

CREATE TABLE Algorithm_Results (
    Result_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Algorithm_ID INT NOT NULL,
    Execution_Date DATE,
    Result_Description TEXT,
    Execution_Status VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (Algorithm_ID) REFERENCES Quantum_Algorithms(Algorithm_ID)
);

CREATE TABLE Researchers (
    Researcher_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Researcher_Name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    Research_Area VARCHAR(100),
    Organization VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Research_Papers (
    Paper_ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Paper_Title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    Researcher_ID INT NOT NULL,
    Publication_Date DATE,
    Abstract TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (Researcher_ID) REFERENCES Researchers(Researcher_ID)
);
